conbody.p:
Federal employees and their dependents, consultants, contractors, grantees, and others must use U.S.-flag air carriers for U.S. Government-financed international air travel and transportation of their personal effects or property, if available (Section5 of the International Air Transportation Fair Competitive Practices Act of1974 (
               49 U.S.C.40118
            ) (Fly America Act)).
